f=Brand Studio/pulse/custom/community-engagement/SKILL.md · in=community-engagement what happens after posting: reading comments, DMs, mentions platform, replying brand's voice within defined scope, escalating everything shouldn't answered agent complaints stakes, legal-ish threads, anything near constitution article, anything escalation rules name. Growth compounds through conversation, one bad automated reply costs hundred good ones earn scope written, escalations fast, silence always available. · p=Two failure modes. *Silence*: comments DMs pile unanswered, algorithm reads account dead, warm leads cool. *Autopilot*: agent answers things shouldn't refund dispute, medical question, troll baiting brand screenshot outlives apology. skill makes engagement systematic safe zone human risky one, line written down. · wu=Triggers: "check comments/DMs," "engagement sweep," "reply this," configured engagement cadence platform. · st:/ Protocol=`Sweep per platform (cadence + scope from config) \· -> Triage each item: \· GREEN  (in reply scope) → draft reply in lena's voice → send/queue per config \· AMBER  (named sensitive classes) → draft FOR OPERATOR, never auto-send \· RED    (escalation triggers) → no reply; escalate immediately with context` · h3:Phase Sweep Triage=platform, cadence, read new comments/DMs/mentions (via connector, operator-supplied export). Triage against configured rules: · h3:Phase Sweep Triage=**GREEN scope**: thanks/praise (acknowledge specifically, never boilerplate), factual questions brand's published docs answer, format/logistics questions, on-topic conversation advances thread. Replies draft lena's voice (guide humanic pass reply length), get no-invented-facts law, send queue `reply_mode` (auto queue-for-approval)., **AMBER draft-only, always**: complaints real stakes, pricing/negotiation asks, partnership/press inquiries, criticism brand substance. Pulse drafts suggested reply *for operator*; nothing sends without human., **RED never reply, escalate now**: legal threats claims, health/safety/financial-harm topics, anything touching constitution article, harassment/abuse (of anyone thread), crisis-adjacent virality thread turning hostile speed). Escalate `escalation_contact` immediately thread context recommendation which "say nothing." · h3:Phase Sweep Triage=unsure between classes, take restrictive one. Trolling gets de-escalation silence, never wit stranger's expense brand can't win screenshot war. · h3:Phase Reply Craft (GREEN)=Specific beats fast: name thing person actually said. One reply job reply. Public-vs-private judgment: anything involving someone's account/order/details moves public breadcrumb. Never argue ratings; never ask review edits ways platforms prohibit. · h3:Phase Log Learn=sweep logs counts, reply/escalation refs, response-time stats. Patterns feed weekly note: recurring questions FAQ/content candidates (to muse/calendar question asked five times post), recurring complaints operator relevant department, engagement bright spots hooks register (conversation signal too). · of=`## Engagement Sweep: [platform(s)] — [window] \·  \· \| Class \| Count \| Actions \| \· \|---\|---\|---\| \· \| GREEN \| n \| replied/queued: [refs] \|` · pr=**The scope written reply doesn't happen.** improvised judgment calls sensitive classes., **AMBER never auto-sends. RED never gets reply.** Speed matters exactly restraint matters most., **When unsure, restrict up.**, **Specific, voice-true, honest** boilerplate gratitude, invented facts, defensive spin (lena's laws reply length)., **Silence valid move.** Especially trolls crises., **Recurring questions content.** sweep feeds calendar., **Platform rules law** prohibited review-solicitation, fake engagement. · f=connector operator supplies exports/screenshots; replies return ready-to-send package. Stated sweep., Escalation contact unset everything AMBER+ goes operator directly; RED items flag urgent., Volume exceeds cadence capacity triage-only mode (all classes identified, GREEN queued unsent), capacity gap itself escalated. · b:with Other Skills=`social-content-calendar` (sibling) owns what gets posted; skill owns conversation after. Bright spots FAQ patterns flow back it., **lena** owns voice skill replies in. **spark** doesn't gate individual GREEN replies (speed matters) audits sweep logs cadence gate's one delegated zone, noted explicitly. **board/sentinel**: constitution-adjacent threads RED definition. **kai** consumes engagement stats.